---
import Contador from "./Contador.astro";
---

<section class="h-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-blue-900 flex flex-col">
  <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl text-center lg:py-16 lg:px-12">
    <div
      class="grid grid-col-1 justify-center mx-auto [&>p]:text-xs [&>p]:sm:text-base [&>p]:md:text-lg [&>p]:lg:text-xl [&>p]:xl:text-2xl"
    >
      <h1
        class="mt-20 mb-6 text-3xl font-extrabold leading-none text-slate-700 md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl dark:text-white"
      >
        Clases de Violoncello
      </h1>

      <p
        class="flex flex-grow mx-auto sm:px-16 xl:px-48 mb-8 w-11/12 text-center font-normal text-slate-700 dark:text-gray-400"
      >
        Las clases son individuales y est√°n destinadas a aquellos que quieran
        perfeccionarse o comenzar desde cero.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Contador />

  <div
    class="mt-16 mb-28 mx-auto inline-flex rounded-md shadow-sm
    [&>a]:text-xs [&>a]:sm:text-base [&>a]:md:text-lg [&>a]:lg:text-xl [&>a]:xl:text-2xl
    [&>a]:px-3 [&>a]:py-1 [&>a]:sm:px-4 [&>a]:sm:py-2 [&>a]:md:px-5 [&>a]:md:py-3 [&>a]:lg:px-10 [&>a]:lg:py-4
    [&>a]:font-medium [&>a]:text-gray-900 [&>a]:bg-transparent [&>a]:border-gray-900"
    role="group"
  >
    <a
      href="/#planes"
      class="border rounded-s-lg hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-white dark:border-gray-500 dark:text-white dark:hover:text-gray-300 dark:focus:bg-gray-700"
    >
      Ver Planes
    </a>

    <a
      href="/#contacto"
      class="border-t border-b hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-white dark:border-gray-500 dark:text-white dark:hover:text-gray-300 dark:focus:bg-gray-700"
    >
      Contactar
    </a>

    <a
      href="https://us04web.zoom.us/j/4387764309?pwd=ekVqeTBtUWp1U0hwdVNyU1J3a1NaQT09"
      target="_blank"
      class="border rounded-e-lg hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-white dark:border-gray-500 dark:text-white dark:hover:text-gray-300 dark:focus:bg-gray-700"
    >
      Clase (Zoom)
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
